# Déterminez la taille exacte de chaque dossier de /var d'une manière
# humainement compréhensible suivi du chemin de celui-ci [Commande]
du -sh /var/*

# du = disk usage = gives information about the usage of a specified disk and folder.
# /var/* = the path of each folder in /var
# -s flag = gives the summary (total size) of each folder.
# -h flag = makes it more humanly readable.
# Alternatively, "du -h -d 1 /var" or "du -h --max-depth=1 /var" achieve the same result.
